  "description": "v15: HEADLESS-ONLY (no WebView). All extraction is pure OkHttp, matching the confirmed-working LookMovieHeadlessExtractor pattern. Disabled all Cloudflare-protected servers that require WebView JS-challenge solving (VidFast, CineSrc, Peachify, MultiEmbed, VidSrc.cc/to, VidZee, VidStorm, SmashyStream, Whvx, Hexa, VidSync, etc.) since pure OkHttp cannot solve CF challenges. Kept non-CF servers + enc-dec.app-backed extractors with dedicated headless code (VidLink, Videasy w/ 10 sub-servers, LordFlix w/ 10 sub-servers + hongkong host fix, KissKh). LookMovie fires first for TV shows. Removed dead false positives (vidsrc.net parking, embed.lol store).",
